data.description: Newly listed in the highly desirable Countryside Community in Lebanon! This property features over 5046 SQFT of livable space and is located in a cozy cul-de-sac in the very back of Countryside. Summerwood offers multiple bedrooms, a spacious kitchen, vaulted ceilings, a fully finished basement with additional rooms, new large deck, a deep and wide 2-car garage, and an iron fenced backyard! This home has ample space to entertain friends and family! This neighborhood features a community pool, walking trails, and is a short walk (or jog) away from Countryside YMCA. You'll also be close to the beautiful and historic Downtown Lebanon District which is full of charm and activities for everyone, as well as shopping and eateries. Book your tour today!
